snippet.textDisplay: Jaffer's voice is like honey; thick and sweet and so soothing! One of the most romantic Pakistani male voices in my opinion. I could bliss out listening to him all day. I do prefer when he sings in Urdu over Punjabi though. And even though I loved his voice here I was hoping the song would pick up a little at some point. Hoping there's more to listen to from Kaavish this season. I'm not prepared for Jaffer to sink into oblivion again so soon! I need more!!
